---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Philosophy — Robles Technologies Corp."
  description="Our philosophy: the 3Rs (Redesign, Reinvent, Refocus), fair compensation for all, and the mission, vision, and core values behind every engagement at RTC."
  active="philosophy"
>
  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-pat"></div>
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>Philosophy</div>
    <span class="sec-tag">What We Believe</span>
    <h1 class="sec-h">Built on principles that<br>don't change.</h1>
    <p class="sec-p">Our philosophy isn't a tagline — it's the operating system behind every hire, every engagement, and every deliverable we ship. It starts with three words.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 3Rs SECTION -->
  <section class="phil-r-section">
    <div class="phil-r-pat"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
      <span class="sec-tag" style="color:var(--green);">The 3Rs</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h" style="color:var(--white);">Redesign. Reinvent. Refocus.</h2>
      <p class="sec-p" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);max-width:580px;">Three principles that define how we approach every problem — from the smallest workflow fix to the largest enterprise transformation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="phil-3rs-grid">

      <!-- R1 -->
      <div class="phil-r-card rv">
        <div class="phil-r-num">01</div>
        <div class="phil-r-title">Redesign</div>
        <p class="phil-r-desc">We don't patch broken processes — we rebuild them from the ground up. Surface-level fixes create technical debt and confusion. Real transformation starts at the root.</p>
        <ul class="phil-r-bullets">
          <li>Audit existing workflows before writing a single line of code</li>
          <li>Remove steps that add friction without adding value</li>
          <li>Build systems that are intuitive for the humans who use them every day</li>
          <li>Architect for how your business will look in 2 years, not just today</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- R2 -->
      <div class="phil-r-card rv d1">
        <div class="phil-r-num">02</div>
        <div class="phil-r-title">Reinvent</div>
        <p class="phil-r-desc">Technology moves fast. We stay ahead of it — bringing fresh thinking, AI capabilities, and modern engineering approaches to problems that legacy solutions have failed to solve.</p>
        <ul class="phil-r-bullets">
          <li>Evaluate AI-powered solutions before defaulting to manual approaches</li>
          <li>Challenge assumptions about how your stack needs to work</li>
          <li>Introduce modern tooling where legacy tools are holding you back</li>
          <li>Deliver solutions that transform how your team operates, not just automates what it already does</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- R3 -->
      <div class="phil-r-card rv d2">
        <div class="phil-r-num">03</div>
        <div class="phil-r-title">Refocus</div>
        <p class="phil-r-desc">Streamlined systems return your team's most valuable resource: time and attention. When operations run smoothly, people can focus on what actually grows the business.</p>
        <ul class="phil-r-bullets">
          <li>Measure success by how much manual work we eliminate, not just features shipped</li>
          <li>Empower your team to spend time on strategy, not firefighting</li>
          <li>Build reporting and visibility tools so leadership can make faster decisions</li>
          <li>Create systems that run quietly in the background — the way good infrastructure should</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAIR COMPENSATION -->
  <section class="compensation-section">
    <div class="rv">
      <span class="sec-tag">Fair Compensation for All</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h">The second pillar of<br>everything we build.</h2>
      <p class="sec-p">Fair compensation isn't a benefit at RTC — it's a core operating principle. We believe that the quality of our work is inseparable from how our team is treated.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="compensation-grid">
      <div class="comp-card rv">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Equitable Pay, Always</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Every specialist at RTC is compensated equitably — relative to the value they deliver, the market they operate in, and the outcomes they produce for clients. No exploitation, no undercutting, no exceptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card rv d1">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Global Standards, Local Talent</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">The Philippines produces exceptional IT talent. RTC's mission is to compensate that talent at the level it deserves — and to position our team members as recognized, global-grade professionals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card rv d2">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Compensation Tied to Outcomes</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">We tie compensation to real outcomes — not hours spent. This aligns our incentives with yours: our team wins when you win, which means we're always focused on what actually matters.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card rv">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Built to Retain Excellence</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Consistency in quality delivery requires consistency in team retention. By paying fairly, we keep our best people engaged and growing — so you always work with specialists at the top of their field.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card rv d1">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Transparent Pricing Reflects This</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Our client-facing pricing is built to be sustainable — covering fair team compensation, reinvestment in capability, and a reasonable margin. You're not overpaying; we're not undervaluing our people.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card rv d2">
        <div class="comp-icon"></div>
        <div class="comp-title">Economic Impact That Compounds</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Every engagement creates economic opportunity. As RTC grows, so does the reach of equitable compensation — creating a compounding positive impact for the communities where our team lives and works.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION & VISION -->
  <section class="sec" style="background:var(--white);">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:52px;align-items:start;">
      <div class="rv">
        <span class="sec-tag">Our Mission</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h">Why RTC exists.</h2>
        <p class="sec-p">To bridge global opportunities with expert talent by delivering innovative technology and consulting solutions — built on trust, precision, and fair partnership.</p>
        <p class="sec-p" style="margin-top:14px;">We exist because businesses deserve a tech partner that treats them as partners — not ticket numbers. And IT professionals deserve a platform that treats them as the global-grade talent they are.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv d1">
        <span class="sec-tag">Our Vision</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h">Where we're going.</h2>
        <p class="sec-p">To become a global platform that elevates IT professionals and showcases the Philippines as a premier destination for technology expertise and digital innovation.</p>
        <p class="sec-p" style="margin-top:14px;">We're building RTC to be the firm that proves you don't need to overpay a large agency or tolerate low-quality offshore delivery. Expert execution, fair teams, and real results — that's the model.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES GRID -->
  <section class="about-values-full sec" id="values">
    <div class="rv" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px;">
      <span class="sec-tag">Core Values</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h">The principles behind<br>every decision we make</h2>
      <p class="sec-p" style="margin:0 auto;">These aren't aspirational statements. They're the operating principles behind every decision, every hire, and every client engagement we take on.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-full-grid">
      <div class="value-full-card rv"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Fair Compensation</div><p class="vfc-desc">Equitable pay for every team member — always. This is how we attract and keep exceptional talent, and how we ensure the quality of every deliverable we ship.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d1"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Precision Execution</div><p class="vfc-desc">Outcomes-first delivery. Every solution is built to be scalable, reliable, and easy to maintain. We obsess over the details so your team doesn't have to.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d2"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Global Standards</div><p class="vfc-desc">We operate to the same standard as the top-tier global technology firms — without the overhead. World-class execution, accessible pricing.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d3"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">True Partnership</div><p class="vfc-desc">We don't fill tickets. We embed with your business, understand your goals, and build solutions that create long-term value — not just short-term deliverables.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Transparency First</div><p class="vfc-desc">Fixed-price proposals. No hidden fees. No surprises. You know exactly what you're getting before a single hour of work begins.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d1"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Growth Mindset</div><p class="vfc-desc">We're a startup — and proud of it. We move fast, learn constantly, and build the kind of agile team that can solve problems larger firms can't.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d2"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">AI-Forward</div><p class="vfc-desc">AI is central to how we think, build, and advise. We bring practical AI capabilities to every client — not hype, but real solutions that move the needle.</p></div>
      <div class="value-full-card rv d3"><div class="vfc-icon"></div><div class="vfc-title">Community Impact</div><p class="vfc-desc">Every role at RTC creates economic opportunity and global visibility for IT professionals. That impact compounds with every project we deliver.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-final">
    <div class="cta-pat"></div>
    <div class="cta-glow"></div>
    <div class="cta-content">
      <span class="sec-tag" style="color:var(--green);">Work With a Team That Believes This</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h" style="color:var(--white);margin-top:8px;">Ready to build something together?</h2>
      <p class="sec-p" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);margin:0 auto 32px;">Every engagement starts with a free discovery call. Let's scope your project and send you a fixed-price proposal within 48 hours — no commitment required.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/kenneth-roblestech/30min'});return false;" class="btn btn-white">Book a Call →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-ghost">View Services</a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-hint" style="margin-top:16px;">Or reach us at <a href="mailto:contact@roblestech.net">contact@roblestech.net</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
